title: Bob Dylan & Johnny Cash - Nashville 1969 [FLAC]
description:
One of the most famous bootlegs ever: The legendary Nashville sessions by Bob Dylan & Johnny Cash. Until now only two tracks were released officially: Track 1 on a Johnny Cash video entitled "Johnny Cash, The Man And His Music". Track 9 on various compilations, for example on the 4CD-Box-Set "Johnny Cash - The Legend" (2005). Unbelievable, that these amazing duets of Bob & Johnny were never released officially.


Bob Dylan & Johnny Cash - Nashville 1969
a.k.a The Nashville Sessions or The Dylan/Cash Sessions
Label: Yellow Dog - YD 049 
Format: CD, Unofficial Release
Released: 1994


Unofficial Studio Recording - Excellent Sound Quality


Tracks 1-16 recorded at CBS Studio A, Nashville, TN February 17 & 18, 1969 
Tracks 17-19 recorded for the Cash Show, Ryman Auditorium, Nashville, TN May 1, 1969
